Eagle River to buy French company . AVON , Colo , Nov 25 - Eagle River Interactive said on Monday it agreed to buy the assets of Groupe SRC , a Paris - based company specializing in multimedia localization for an undisclosed amount of cash . Eagle River said the purchase , which is expected to be completed within the next four weeks , will provide it with an opportunity to expand in Europe . Eagle River said it is currently working with Disneyland Paris , for example , to develop a Web site that is localized in six languages , French , English , German , Spanish , Italian and Dutch . 
